Open another Terminal by clicking + and run 'npm install -g json-server', then run 'npx json-server --watch data/db.json --port 8000'. This terminal should not be closed.
Go back to the first terminal and run 'npm run start'
For more info copy paste this link 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eao7ABGFUXs&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9gZD-Tvwfod2gaISzfRiP9d&index=16' 
